data.description: RARE FIND!!! This two year old Caledonia home is ready for it's new owner. This three bedroom two bath home features an office, granite in the kitchen with an island open to the living room, seperate formal dining room, large master bath with a tiled shower, patio,  two car garage, a HUGE 30x40 wired shop, and 3.10+/- acres.
